[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "夜晚的基地本该是静谧的，正常情况下只能隐约听到机器运转的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我却觉得“吵”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自从拔掉了耶洛沙的树后，那些嘈杂的声音和纷乱的影像就时不时出现在我的脑中。到了夜晚，这种症状似乎有加剧的势头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这段时间，我很难入睡，更别说即便是睡着了也容易被噩梦侵扰。枪声，尖叫，无尽的雪原和刺眼的鲜红在不停地搅动着我的大脑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这些都是暂时的症状，在医疗部的帮助下我会慢慢好起来，只不过当下实在是有些令人困扰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一阵窸窸窣窣的声音自耳边响起，黑暗中显得尤为鲜明，脑中的杂音随即被驱散，如潮水般退却。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个时间，还在零食柜拿东西吃的，就只有……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔，你怎么又不开灯？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Mo_girl003_embarrassed01_054",
        "zh_CN": "啊哈哈……是分析员啊，吓我一跳。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我这不是饿了，只想着找点东西赶紧填饱肚子……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "喂，你没事吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随着大厅的灯光亮起，我们看清了彼此的脸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你的脸色看上去有点糟糕，你也饿了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "来，这包饼干给你吃，别客气！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这可是经我评测零食柜里最好吃的饼干。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "谢谢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我只是睡不着，随便出来走走。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员失眠了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那怎么行！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "吃饱和睡好是同等级别的要紧事，人一旦饿了困了就会心情不好，还会生病！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔的表情肉眼可见地慌张起来，接着她蹙起眉头陷入思索。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想想……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呜……有了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，跟我来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔不由分说地抓起我的手朝着她房间的方向走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的手很温暖，手指细长而有力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一般我睡不着的时候就想做点能流汗的运动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哦？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个时间训练室已经关闭了，不过……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔房间内的健身角二十四小时为分析员开放！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "原来，妮塔拉我来是想让我健身，睡前适当的运动确实有助于改善睡眠质量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这些健身器械有频繁使用的痕迹，在训练方面，她从未松懈过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "或许正因为大量的训练，才导致她更容易陷入饥饿，晚餐的热量不足以满足她的需求。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员可以先从伸展运动开始，接着再做一些轻度的肌肉练习。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然，我会全程陪着你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "半夜被队员拉到房间里一起健身，哪怕对我来说也是一种新奇的体验，有点令人哭笑不得。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那就拜托妮塔了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一段时间后——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "感觉如何？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "很畅快，整个人松弛了下来，又不是特别累。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是吧，是吧~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我仿佛看到一只马里努阿犬在疯狂地摇动尾巴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "适度的肌肉训练不仅能舒缓身体，心灵的杂质也会随着汗水一起排出体外。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看来，这方面你倒是挺有心得。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿嘿，那是当然。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你快仔细看看我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "今晚妮塔独家放送，分析员可以先从这里开始检查我的健身成果。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这番胡闹下来，先前通过运动酝酿出的些许睡意消失得无影无踪，可我心里面倒是轻松了不少。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔难得安静地看着我，脸上挂着微笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
